               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Saint Peter, ጸሎተ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡; Asmat Prayer, “I Beseech You Lest I die Early,” ተማኅጸንኩ: ከመ: ኢይሙት: ዘእንበለ: ጊዜየ:; Sword of Divinity, ሠይፈ፡ መለኮት፡, Asmat Prayer of the Seven Archangels, ድርሳን፡ ዘሰባቱ፡ ሊቃነ፡ መላእክት፡; Asmat Prayers against Demon, to Lure a Lover, against Evil eye and Epilepsy, to Weaken the Power of Kings, for Protection; Prayer against the Tongue of People, ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝʿǝz</textLang>
