                     </title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                     <locus from="34v" facs="039">Fols 34v and following</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Evil Eye and Epilepsy, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይነት፡ ባሪያ፡ ገርጋሪ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይነት፡ ባሪያ፡ ገርጋሪ፡ ካፍ፡ ካፍ፡ ካፍ፡ ካፍ፡ ካፍ፡ ካፍ፡ ካፍ፡ ላፍ፡ ላፍ፡ ላፍ፡ ላፍ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
